    "description": "恶魔依然活着一款充满残酷动作的类银河战士恶魔平台游戏，采用高技巧的战斗机制，设定在恶魔的噩梦世界中。探索世界，升级你的能力，释放火与冰的力量，消灭阻挡你命运的敌人。征服一切迎面而来的挑战。<br><br>激烈战斗：利用新获得的技能与复杂的连招消灭所有敌人，运用特殊招式清扫你的前进道路。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033190/extras/d2824c56a4bf076a6f33a32b10e555c7.poster.avif?t=1770199348\" width=632 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033190/extras/d2824c56a4bf076a6f33a32b10e555c7.webm?t=1770199348\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033190/extras/d2824c56a4bf076a6f33a32b10e555c7.mp4?t=1770199348\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>见证利刃之力：释放冰与火的愤怒，以及利刃本身的力量，击败你的敌人。获得毁灭性的全新连招和特殊技巧，一路净化敌人。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033190/extras/5d3cba65811ea91b0c85fba19dcbab44.poster.avif?t=1770199348\" width=632 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033190/extras/5d3cba65811ea91b0c85fba19dcbab44.webm?t=1770199348\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033190/extras/5d3cba65811ea91b0c85fba19dcbab44.mp4?t=1770199348\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>激战Boss战：成群的巨大扭曲恶魔阻挡你的目标。学习它们的动作，承受其毁灭性的攻击，并赢得胜利。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033190/extras/2fe396e26483a8791493dae61cb29808.poster.avif?t=1770199348\" width=632 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033190/extras/2fe396e26483a8791493dae61cb29808.webm?t=1770199348\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"http